 Paris Saint-Germain F.C. season|2013\u201314]]\n|Ligue 1\n|16||2||2||0||4||0||4{{efn|name=ucl}}||0||0||0||26||2 \n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!79!!14!!8!!0!!7!!1!!16!!4!!0!!0!!110!!19\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[A.C. Milan]]\n|[[2014\u201315 A.C. Milan season|2014\u201315]]\n|Serie A\n|33||16||1||0||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||34||16\n|-\n|[[2015\u201316 A.C. Milan season|2015\u201316]]\n|Serie A\n|10||2||2||2||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||12||4\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!43!!18!!3!!2!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!46!!20\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[FC Girondins de Bordeaux|Bordeaux]]\n|[[2016\u201317 FC Girondins de Bordeaux season|2016\u201317]]\n|Ligue 1\n|26||3||3||0||2||0||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||31||3\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!26!!3!!3!!0!!2!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!31!!3\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Antalyaspor]]\n|[[2017\u201318 S\u00fcper Lig|2017\u201318]]\n|[[S\u00fcper Lig]]\n|7||0||0||0||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||7||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!7!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!7!!0\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Club Am\u00e9rica|Am\u00e9rica]]\n|[[2017\u201318 Liga MX season|2017\u201318]]\n|[[Liga MX]]\n|11||5||colspan=2|\u2014||colspan=2|\u2014||1{{efn|Appearances in the [[CONCACAF Champions League]].}}||0||colspan=2|\u2014||12||5\n|-\n|[[2018-19 Club Am\u00e9rica season|2018-19]]\n|[[Liga MX]]\n|6\n|0\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n|6\n|0\n|-\n|[[2019\u201320 Club Am\u00e9rica season|2019-20]]\n|[[Liga MX]]\n|1\n|0\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n|1\n|0\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" |Total\n!17\n!5\n!0\n!0\n!0\n!0\n!1\n!0\n!0\n!0\n!19\n!5\n|-\n|[[Paris FC]]\n|[[2019-20 Paris FC Season|2019-20]]\n|[[Ligue 2]]\n|17\n|4\n|1\n|1\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n|18\n|5\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!351!!66!!24!!2!!14!!1!!42!!9!!1!!0!!468!!85\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n===International===\n<!-- NOTE: when updating stats, update the infobox too! -->\n{{Updated|26 March 2013}}<ref name=\"NFT\">{{NFT player|id=39483}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=3|[[France national football team|France national team]]\n|-\n! Year !! Apps !! Goals\n|-\n| 2010 || 2 || 0\n|-\n| 2011 || 7 || 0\n|-\n| 2012 || 12 || 2\n|-\n| 2013 || 3 || 0\n|-\n! Total !! 24 !! 2\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''Scores and results list France's goal tally first.''<ref name=\"NFT\"/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! No. !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1 || 5 June 2012 || [[MMArena]], Le Mans, France || {{fb|EST}} || align=center | 4\u20130 || align=center | 4\u20130 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 2 || 15 June 2012 || [[Donbass Arena]], Donetsk, Ukraine || {{fb|UKR}} || align=center | 1\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20130 || [[UEFA Euro 2012 Group D|UEFA Euro 2012]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Paris Saint-Germain'''\n*[[Ligue 1]]: [[2012\u201313 Ligue 1|2012\u201313]], [[2013\u201314 Ligue 1|2013\u201314]]<ref name=ligue1/>\n*[[Coupe de la Ligue]]: [[2013\u201314 Coupe de la Ligue|2013\u201314]]<ref name=ligue1/>\n\n'''Am\u00e9rica'''\n*[[Liga MX]]: [[2018\u201319 Liga MX season|Apertura 2018]]\n*[[Copa MX]]: [[Clausura 2019 Copa MX|Clausura 2019]]\n*[[Campe\u00f3n de Campeones]]: [[2019 Campe\u00f3n de Campeones|2019]]\n\n'''France U17'''\n*[[UEFA European Under-17 Championship]]: [[2004 UEFA European Under-17 Championship|2004]]<ref name=ligue1/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{LFP}}\n* {{Lequipe}}\n\n{{Paris FC squad}}\n{{France squad UEFA Euro 2012}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Menez, Jeremy}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Longjumeau]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Essonne]]\n[[Category:French footballers]]\n[[Category:France international footballers]]\n[[Category:France youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:France under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Association football wingers]]\n[[Category:FC Sochaux-Montb\u00e9liard players]]\n[[Category:AS Monaco FC players]]\n[[Category:A.S. Roma players]]\n[[Category:Paris Saint-Germain F.C. players]]\n[[Category:A.C. Milan players]]\n[[Category:FC Girondins de Bordeaux players]]\n[[Category:Antalyaspor footballers]]\n[[Category:Club Am\u00e9rica footballers]]\n[[Category:Paris FC players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 1 players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:Liga MX players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 2 players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2012 players]]\n[[Category:French expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:French expatriate sportspeople in Monaco]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Monaco]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n[[Category:French expatriate sportspeople in Italy]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n[[Category:French expatriate sportspeople in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Mexico]]\n[[Category:French expatriate sportspeople in Mexico]]\n", "text_old": "{{EngvarB|date=October 2017}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2017}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = J\u00e9r\u00e9my M\u00e9nez\n| image = J\u00e9r\u00e9my M\u00e9nez.jpg\n| image_size = \n| caption = M\u00e9nez playing for [[FC Girondins de Bordeaux|Bordeaux]] in 2016\n| fullname = J\u00e9r\u00e9my M\u00e9nez<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tff.org/Default.aspx?pageId=526&kisiId=2017828 |title=Jeremy Menez |publisher=Turkish Football Federation |accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref>\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1987|5|7|df=y}}<ref name=Lequipe>{{cite news |url=https://www.lequipe.fr/Football/FootballFicheJoueur20434.html |title=J\u00e9r\u00e9my M\u00e9nez |newspaper=L'\u00c9quipe |location=Paris |accessdate=20 January 2020 |language=French}}</ref>\n| birth_place = [[Longjumeau]], France\n| height = 1.83 m<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.clubamerica.com.mx/jugador/jeremy-menez/|title=Club Am\u00e9rica|first=Club|last=Am\u00e9rica|publisher=clubamerica.com.mx}}</ref>\n|